title: Je T'aime Moi Non Plus 1976 Jane Birkin, Joe Dallesandro, Hugues Quester, Reinhard Kolldehoff, Maite Nahyr, Liliane Rovere, Gillian Gill, Josiane Leveque, Doris Thomas, Cluadia Butenuth + Serge Gainsbourg

sources.title: Je T'aime Moi Non Plus 1976 Jane Birkin, Joe Dallesandro, Hugues Quester, Reinhard Kolldehoff, Maite Nahyr, Liliane Rovere, Gillian Gill, Josiane Leveque, Doris Thomas, Cluadia Butenuth + Serge Gainsbourg
sources.description: From IMDB: Petite waitress Johnny works and lives in a truck-stop, where she's lonely and longs for love. She develops a crush on garbage-truck driver Krassky, although her sleazy boss Boris warns her that he's gay. ---- This one may still fall into the French New Wave genre, it is atmospheric and slow moving. All of the characters have a rather desperate aspect to them, but managed to be interesting rather than repellent.
